###How many batches with $2.25\,\text{kg}$ of sugar?

Let's find the value of $b$ when $s=\blueE{2.25}$:

$\begin{align}
b&=\dfrac{s}{0.3}
\\\\
b&=\dfrac{\blueE{2.25}}{0.3}
\\\\
b&=7.5
\end{align}$

###How long to gain $200$ total XP?

Let's find the value of $t$ when $p=\blueE{200}$:

$\begin{align}
t&=\dfrac{p}{12.5}
\\\\
t&=\dfrac{\blueE{200}}{12.5}
\\\\
t&=16
\end{align}$
